system.name: Foiling Foliage
system.effect:
Target: Your Pokémon with a Grass-Type Status Move
Effect: Pick a Grass-Type Status-Class Move known by the target. The chosen Move no longer takes up a Move Slot. A Pokémon may have only one Move bypass the Move Limit at a time; if a new Move is chosen for a Pokémon, the previous Move loses this effect.
system.prerequisites: Type Ace, Grass as Chosen Type
